import React from 'react'
import { Text, View, Pressable } from 'react-native'
import { LinearGradient } from 'expo-linear-gradient'
import colors from '../../assets/colors/colors'
import { SafeAreaView } from 'react-native-safe-area-context'
import { StatusBar } from 'expo-status-bar'
import UserList from '../social/UserList'

export default function Social() {    
    return (
        <LinearGradient colors={[colors.lightBlue, colors.darkBlue]} style={styles.outerScreen}>
            <SafeAreaView style={styles.contentCenter}>
                <StatusBar barStyle='light-content' />
                <Text style = {styles.pageHeader}>Social</Text>
                <View style={styles.innerScreen}>
                    <View style={styles.topNav}>
                        <Pressable style={styles.navLink} title="Users List" onPress={() => console.log("Button 1 clicked")}>
                            <Text>Users List</Text>
                        </Pressable>
                        <Pressable style={styles.navLink} title="Friend Requests" onPress={() => console.log("Button 2 clicked")}>
                            <Text>Friend Requests</Text>
                        </Pressable>
                    </View>
                    <UserList />
                </View>
            </SafeAreaView>
        </LinearGradient>
    );
}   

const styles = {
    outerScreen: {
        position: 'absolute',
        left: 0,
        right: 0,
        top: 0,
        height: '100%'
    },
    pageHeader: {
        fontSize: 30,
        fontFamily: 'NunitoSans-Bold',
        color: '#000000'
    },
    contentCenter: {
        height: '100%',
        alignItems: 'center'
    },
    innerScreen: {
        height: '95%',
        width: '100%',
        backgroundColor: "#FFFFFF",
        borderRadius: 0
    },
    topNav: {
        flexDirection: 'row',
        justifyContent: 'space-between',
        width: '100%',
        padding: '5px'
    },
    navLink: {
        backgroundColor: '#ccc',
        borderRadius: '5px',
        paddingTop: '10px',
        paddingBottom: '10px',
        width: '49.5%',
        textAlign: 'center'
    }
}
